**HELL YES. You’re wiring this beast for programmatic control.**  
You’re about to get a **full JSON function schema** so you (or another system) can interact with LoreBot via function calling — think: custom GPT integration, agent routing, or external tools triggering commands via schema.

---

## 🧠 What This Schema Does

This is a **machine-readable definition** of all LoreBot's key functions:  
> Slash commands, bot triggers, and mod ops — mapped cleanly into a JSON schema.

You can feed this into:
- Custom GPTs (function-calling or plugin schema)
- Discord mod AI agents
- Backend tools for triggering flags/intel/summaries

---

## 📦 FUNCTION SCHEMA: `lorebot_schema.json`

```json
{
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "submit_flag",
      "description": "Logs a red flag report on a specific user",
      "parameters": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "target_user_id": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "The Discord user ID of the person being flagged"
          },
          "reason": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Detailed reason or quote for flag"
          },
          "severity": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": ["low", "medium", "high"],
            "description": "Severity level for escalation and threading"
          },
          "anonymous": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "description": "If true, hides the flag submitter's identity"
          }
        },
        "required": ["target_user_id", "reason"]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "generate_user_intel",
      "description": "Returns a behavioral profile for a specific user",
      "parameters": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "user_id": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Discord user ID to analyze"
          }
        },
        "required": ["user_id"]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "post_as_bot",
      "description": "Shadow-post a message into the quotes channel via the bot",
      "parameters": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "channel_id": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Target Discord channel ID for the message"
          },
          "message": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Content to post as the bot"
          }
        },
        "required": ["channel_id", "message"]
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "panic_vc_alert",
      "description": "Triggers a mod-ping and alert that someone is being targeted or unsafe in VC",
      "parameters": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "context": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Optional context or quote describing the incident"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "summarize_lore",
      "description": "Generates a lore summary from a DM dump or thread",
      "parameters": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "source_text": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Message content or discussion dump to summarize"
          },
          "tone": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": ["serious", "satirical", "neutral", "dark humor"],
            "description": "Desired tone of the summary"
          }
        },
        "required": ["source_text"]
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

